{
  "id": "f0c603eb1dd44d0c9051a2f378526a7a",
  "title": "App And Gamepad Utils",
  "description": "Use this plugin to handle the major app and gamepad events",
  "longDescription": "<p>This plugin will help you to make your game more comfortable for a player. For example, pause the game when gamepad is disconnected or game is minimized. There is also other helpful functions.</p><p><br /></p><p>You can ask me to implement other functions to this plugin.</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<blockquote><strong>Usage</strong> <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XxIXSqZcCdEO9br2RfS3A8PIKkyVrNgxJoR02fA9yuY/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>read this document</strong></a></blockquote><blockquote>You need to configure another plugin to support controllers other than XBox&#39;s for PC. However, if your game uses Steam, you just need to enable Steam input and your game will work with both XBox and PS gamepads.</blockquote><p><br /></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li>Easy to integrate</li><li>Watch and handle the gamepad events such as connected/disconnected and pairing</li><li>Pause the game when app is minimized/lost focus</li><li>Check the external UI status</li><li>Helpful functions to read your input key mappings (taking into account gamepad status)</li><li>Supports the consoles (console version by request)</li></ul><p><strong>Code Modules:</strong></p><ul><li>Â AppAndGamepadUtils [Runtime]</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 1</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 3</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: All</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: All</p>",
